text: Wan Mohd Khalmizam bin Wan Abdul Aziz (born 21 August 1986) is an archer from Malaysia. Khalmizam competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics.Wan KhalmizamWan KHALMIZAM == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian archers Category:Olympians for Malaysia Category:People from Kelantan
